results.abstract: Cosmos XLI, XLII and XLIII launched; latter 2 put into identical orbits by single rocket

headline.main: SOVIET LAUNCHES THREE SATELLITES; 2 of Unmanned Craft Put in Orbit by One Rocket

results.snippet: MOSCOW, Aug. 22 (UPI) -- The Soviet Union today launched three unmanned earth satellites, the second time it has done this in four days.
results.lead_paragraph: MOSCOW, Aug. 22 (UPI) -- The Soviet Union today launched three unmanned earth satellites, the second time it has done this in four days.
